inlineContent.text: This container contains types and functions for the Data Protection Keychain of iOS and macOS.
Use the functionality provided in the
container for file based keychains of macOS.
Trying to use the methods for the Data Protection Keychain in macOS applications without an application ID will cause your app to crash with a fatal error.
Such macOS applications do not have access to the Data Protection Keychain.

For this purpose, both iOS and macOS offer a system keychain.
